propel.core.collections.maps.avl

Class AvlHashtable<TKey extends java.lang.Comparable<TKey>,TValue>

  • java.lang.Object
    • propel.core.collections.maps.avl.AvlHashtable<TKey,TValue>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<KeyValuePair<TKey,TValue>>, IHashtable<TKey,TValue>, ReifiedMap<TKey,TValue>

    public class AvlHashtable<TKey extends java.lang.Comparable<TKey>,TValue>
extends java.lang.Object
implements IHashtable<TKey,TValue>
    A type-aware AVL-tree-backed hashtable. This map does not allow null keys to be inserted.
